{"tid":1285411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"從有人自稱要跳樓，再到死左人先無啦啦出post話有人因反送中自殺，我正式宣布","createTime":"2019-07-04T14:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T10:36:29.000Z","uid":32051,"like":57,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"4caf19bd45859c557add70a10bff1d69c5b2ad60","tid":1285411,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有反送中同路人<br />\n對唔住，你地已經畀港共黑警剝削埋你地自殺既權利</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港共麻目不仁，不斷利用大家香港正常人既惻隱之心。<br />\n大家尋日搵足果件jj chan一日，心情幾近崩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好明顯，港共知大家對每一位同路人都好上心。<br />\n對每一個獨立既生命都好在乎，所以港共開始利用自殺去影響軍心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港共草菅人命，喪心病狂到搵死人/自殺去刺激反送中同路人。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我正式宣布，邊個再自殺/提自殺都是敵人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為敵人睇穿我地有人性，而佢地無，所以佢地利用依樣野大做文章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，我改口。<br />\n唔再講唔好死。<br />\n唔好死，係求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家係代所有反送中同路人講：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔准死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"d119510cce4abe21dfaffff530974fd6bba77e0c","tid":1285411,"uid":32051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"唔准死<br />\n<br />\n邊個死邊個就係敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b01f5eca1fb77cd4cb82ae7e518cda9d00a50f","tid":1285411,"uid":192726,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"d119510cce4abe21dfaffff530974fd6bba77e0c","tid":1285411,"uid":32051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"re